Q2

PC 1 : ip 192.168.1.2/24 192.168.1.1
PC 2 : ip 192.168.2.2/24 192.168.2.1
PC 3 : ip 192.168.3.2/24 192.168.3.1
PC 4 : ip 192.168.4.2/24 192.168.4.1
PC 5 : ip 192.168.5.2/24 192.168.5.1


Router 1: 

Router> enable
Router# configure terminal

Router(config)# interface fastethernet0/0
Router(config-if)# ip address 192.168.1.1 255.255.255.0
Router(config-if)# no shutdown
Router(config-if)# exit

Router(config)# interface fastethernet0/1
Router(config-if)# ip address 192.168.2.1 255.255.255.0
Router(config-if)# no shutdown
Router(config-if)# exit

Router(config)# interface serial1/0
Router(config-if)# ip address 11.0.0.1 255.255.255.0
Router(config-if)# no shutdown
Router(config-if)# exit

Router(config)#ip routing
Router(config)#ip route 192.168.3.0 255.255.255.0 11.0.0.2
Router(config)#ip route 192.168.4.0 255.255.255.0 11.0.0.2
Router(config)#ip route 192.168.5.0 255.255.255.0 11.0.0.2
Router(config)#ip route 12.0.0.0 255.255.255.0 11.0.0.2

Router(config)# exit
Router# copy running-config startup-config

Router 2:
 
Same but with :
Router(config)# interface fastethernet0/0
Router(config-if)# ip address 192.168.3.1 255.255.255.0

Router(config)# interface serial1/0
Router(config-if)# ip address 11.0.0.2 255.255.255.0

Router(config)# interface serial1/1
Router(config-if)# ip address 12.0.0.1 255.255.255.0

Router(config)#ip route 192.168.1.0 255.255.255.0 11.0.0.1
Router(config)#ip route 192.168.2.0 255.255.255.0 11.0.0.1
Router(config)#ip route 192.168.4.0 255.255.255.0 12.0.0.2
Router(config)#ip route 192.168.5.0 255.255.255.0 12.0.0.2
Router(config)#ip routing

Router 3: 

Same but with :
Router(config)# interface fastethernet0/0
Router(config-if)# ip address 192.168.4.1 255.255.255.0

Router(config)# interface fastethernet0/1
Router(config-if)# ip address 192.168.5.1 255.255.255.0

Router(config)# interface serial1/0
Router(config-if)# ip address 12.0.0.2 255.255.255.0

Router(config)#ip route 192.168.1.0 255.255.255.0 12.0.0.1
Router(config)#ip route 192.168.2.0 255.255.255.0 12.0.0.1
Router(config)#ip route 192.168.3.0 255.255.255.0 12.0.0.1
Router(config)#ip route 11.0.0.0 255.255.255.0 12.0.0.1
Router(config)#ip routing
